<div id="review_47685026" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/47685026" />
    <a title="Chana" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/1400289-chana"><img alt="Chana" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1373441206p2/1400289.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/47685026?book_show_action=true">Feb 27, 2009</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Chana" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Chana" href="/user/show/1400289-chana">Chana</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1400289-chana?shelf=memoirs-and-biographies">memoirs-and-biographies</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1400289-chana?shelf=short-stories">short-stories</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer47685026" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2273137316219486044">Funny, sweet, charming vignettes of an unusual lifestyle. The author is a 1st grade teacher and I wonder if she isn&apos;t a bit like Miss Frizzle of The Magic School Bus. She takes alligators in stride and her mother can sleep outside calmly during a hurricane. It was worth reading. </span>
  <span id="freeText2273137316219486044" style="display:none">Funny, sweet, charming vignettes of an unusual lifestyle. The author is a 1st grade teacher and I wonder if she isn't a bit like Miss Frizzle of The Magic School Bus. She takes alligators in stride and her mother can sleep outside calmly during a hurricane. It was worth reading. </span>
  <a data-text-id="2273137316219486044" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
