        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer918233005" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2359771183173149909">I loved every piece in this short collection. Each one was like picking a piece of chocolate from a box, rationing them out so they would last longer. Then, Oh No! The box is empty! I&apos;m done. Fortunately there&apos;s another collection to be read.<br/>These essays about her life in Georgia were written 20 years ago, and don&apos;t feel dated at all. I can read them in another 20 years and I bet they will still retain their freshness. You can&apos;t say that about a box of chocolates.</span>
  <span id="freeText2359771183173149909" style="display:none">I loved every piece in this short collection. Each one was like picking a piece of chocolate from a box, rationing them out so they would last longer. Then, Oh No! The box is empty! I'm done. Fortunately there's another collection to be read.<br />These essays about her life in Georgia were written 20 years ago, and don't feel dated at all. I can read them in another 20 years and I bet they will still retain their freshness. You can't say that about a box of chocolates.</span>
